  "text": "Martell (2014) writes that had he been Adam's psychologist, he may have opted against a course of integrative, affirmative cognitive-behavioral treatment, and instead have provided LGB-affirming behavioral activation treatment exclusively. Indeed, behavioral activation, an effective treatment for depression and avoidance [CITATION_1] , may have been an excellent treatment approach with Adam.",
